{"tid":471540,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[一人一票] 如果你養既狗仔老左/病左，你會點做?","createTime":"2017-11-17T10:55:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-17T10:55:07.000Z","uid":86461,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9b1ae357b94e75118ed83aa78c92ba0dd66d5736","tid":471540,"uid":86461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T10:55:07.000Z","msg":"天生忠誠、善良既狗仔，一旦認定你係佢嘅主人，無論你貧窮與富貴，都一定會對你忠誠不二，追隨一生。狗仔既生命只有短暫嘅十幾年，當你活力無限、能跑善跳嘅好夥伴慢慢變得步履蹣跚又或者患病既時候，你會選擇點做?<br />\n<br />\n帶佢睇醫生，繼續照顧佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比佢安樂死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/W88E5DT21768w/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FW88E5DT21768w%2Fgiphy.gif&h=eec1293b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/bWS1Vh9mVkcZq/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FbWS1Vh9mVkcZq%2Fgiphy.gif&h=9df594f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3GPbOod9GkC5i/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3GPbOod9GkC5i%2Fgiphy.gif&h=49914a14&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}